title: Find Your Way Around the FME Academy

questions.question: What’s a module?
options: A series of hands-on steps to implement a feature
A data integration project for you to work on and submit
A series of topics that help you learn a new skill, product, or role
A single learning topic on one page

questions.question: How do you advance ranks?
options: By seniority: The longer you’ve had a Trailhead account, the higher your rank is.
You earn points and badges by completing modules.
You work your way through an entire trail.
